<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Campaign Participation</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        body, h1, p, a {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Body styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Container styles */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f3f0f0da;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24) 0px 3px 8px;
        }

        /* Heading styles */
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        /* Paragraph styles */
        p {
            color: #555555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Link styles */
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Button styles */
        button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: none;
        }

        button:hover {    
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        /* Strong styles */
        strong {
            color: #333333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Logo styles */
        .logo {
            display: block;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .flexed_data {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="flexed_data">
            <img src="https://alwaleed-cyber-quiz.vercel.app/logo192.png" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
            <h2>Company</h2>
        </div>
        <h1>Hello there</h1>
        <p>Please click the following button to change the password:</p>
        <a href="<%= redirectLink %>"><button>Change password</button></a>
        <p>If you did not expect to receive this email or have any questions, please contact us or ignore it.</p>
        <p>Thank you,<br><strong>Company Ltd.</strong></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
